    {
      "chinese": "在部落會遇到的犯罪行有下列七項：第一，誤殺致死罪；第二，毆打傷害罪；第三，搶奪、竊盜罪；第四，侵占、詐欺罪；第五，謊言背信罪；第六，不孝、犯上罪；第七，強姦、通姦罪。",
      "ab": "O mamalitemoh a ’ilo^ i niyaro’ no Pangcah i, pito^.\r\nSakacecay, o pakasero’ay a mipatay to tamdaw. Sakatosa^, o mipadokaay a mipalo^ to tamadaw. \r\nSakatolo^, o mi’afasay ato mitakaway to dafong. \r\nSakasepat, o mikecoay to omah ato misafana’ay to dafong. Sakalima^, o misamangahay to dafong. \r\nSakaenem, caayay pingodo^ to mato’asay a midimokos. Sakapito^, mi’odangay ato masasi’odangay.",
